reviewText:
Request this FREE from one of Jehovahs witnesses  OR you can use the contact form(for a bible study)at jw org so you can be contacted and ask for this

Also there are other videos along this line that you can watch and download for FREE..  this one isn't up there yet but for the others just go to jw dot org
on the bottom right click on "watch sign language videos"
you can choose whatever sign language you prefer
